
Query1:
----------
select distinct num as consecutivenums
from (  
    select
        num,
        lag(num,1) over (order by id desc) as prev1,
        lag(num,2) over (order by id desc) as prev2
    from logs
    )t
    where num=prev1 and num=prev2

Input: 
Logs table:
+----+-----+
| id | num |
+----+-----+
| 1  | 1   |
| 2  | 1   |
| 3  | 1   |
| 4  | 2   |
| 5  | 1   |
| 6  | 2   |
| 7  | 2   |
+----+-----+
Output: 
+-----------------+
| ConsecutiveNums |
+-----------------+
| 1               |
+-----------------+
